#   5. Save .env and run `npm run build && npx cap sync android`
#
# Without step 4, the deployed Cloudflare Worker still hits the old
# project. The two paths are independent: .env drives local dev +
# Capacitor APK builds; Lovable Secrets drive production at
# https://lokali.ge.

